item.title: Great Expectations (The Parody)
item.description: This is a video that was made for an english class that had a project where you needed to make a parody of a book that you had to read. I was not in this class but I helped make this video. Yes I know the specialFX look mostly fake but thats how they're supposed to look. The actors and I were able to produce this entire movie, from planning to exporting ALL with 7 DAYS! Thats amazing for a video this long. I mean, considering it took me like 3 weeks to make 7 minute news cast.
